name: Yo0oNGZ #40
description:
☆ ☆ They are not what you think they are.

We left Juventus x Sassuolo 45 minutes after the game ended. The only cab on the street ha d a grandma inside. We thought she was waiting for somebody to leave the stadium and go home. 

Another cab drove trough and we entered it. The driver in front suddenly stood up and argued with us in Italian. I didn’t understand a single word.

“My mother!” He eventually said.

We ended up talking a lot to the friendly old lady on the cab trip.
